info.author: Guy Teichman
info.name: RNAlysis
info.summary: RNAlysis is a python package providing modular analysis pipeline for RNA sequencing data from C. elegans. The package includes various filtering methods, data visualisation, clustering analyses, enrichment anslyses and exploratory analyses.
